<title>USA: Laidlaw names S. Kennard as CEO.</title>
<headline>Laidlaw names S. Kennard as CEO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-12-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>International investment firm Laidlaw &amp; Co on Monday said it named Stephen Kennard as president and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Kennard replaces Paul Bagley, who sold his shares in the firm to Pacific USA Holdings Corp, a significant investor in Laidlaw, a Laidlaw spokesman sid.</p>
<p>The company also said that Kennard had aquired a stake in the firm.</p>
